<!------------------------------------->
<h1 class="text-center mb-3">Latest Properties</h1>
<section>
    <div class="container card border border-1 border-light pb-4">
        <div class="row">
            @foreach (Ad ad in Model)
            {
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <partial name="_CardPartial" model="ad"></partial>
                </div>
            }
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-primary mx-auto" asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Ad">View More</a>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="py-4 py-xl-5 mb-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-2">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-xl-6 text-center mx-auto">
                <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-5"><span class="pb-3 underline">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)<br></span></h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-5">Got questions? We’ve got answers! Below are some common inquiries about using our platform and how you can maximize your experience with Moghtareb.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-2">
            <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="accordion text-muted" role="tablist" id="accordion-1">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-1">How does a Premium account boost my ad visibility?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse show item-1" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>With a Premium account, your ad gets prioritized in search results, making it more visible to potential buyers. Premium ads are also highlighted with a 'Featured' badge, increasing the chances of attracting attention and receiving inquiries.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-2">How can I track the views and clicks on my ads?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-2" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>As a Premium user, you have access to detailed statistics for your ads, including how many users have viewed your ad and how many clicked to view your contact information. This insight helps you gauge the performance of your listings.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-3">What is a 'Featured' account, and how does it work?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-3" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Upgrading to a 'Featured' account increases your credibility and visibility. Your profile will be marked as 'Featured', allowing potential buyers to trust your listings more readily, and boosting your overall presence on the platform.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" role="tab"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#accordion-1 .item-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1 .item-4">Is there a limit to the number of ads I can post?</button></h2>
                        <div class="accordion-collapse collapse item-4" role="tabpanel" data-bs-parent="#accordion-1">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>There is no limit to the number of ads you can post. However, Premium accounts enjoy additional perks like better ad placement, statistics, and more exposure compared to standard accounts.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

